The Fallen Fapstronauts are the men that have failed to kill the many headed beast called Porn, which now slowly eats them as they toil and scream. This ode is meant to serve as an inspiration for such men and all men who come to read these words of the gods:
Oh, Sing you Muses of these men, the men who tried to fight the immortal monster Porn! The men, who were once so brave and valiant, lured in by the beauty and pleasure of Porn. Like the Sirens, Porn sung sweet promises of ecstasy to even the lowest of us, all of which could be acquired for no work. Oh, if only did we not see how all to good it was!
Oh you poor men, who eventually realized the error of your path. The beautiful forests became deserts of death, the god-like face of Porn a reviling and hideous monster. You tried to fight, tried to run, sword in hand against the beast. Yet the many headed creature would not stop attacking. You poor souls, who were so near victory, gave up and surrendered, to your own laziness and incompetence. Now you lie prisoner as you are slowly eaten alive, watching yourself slowly decade into nothing. At the bottom of the pit you lie, watching other men above you as they tower to heights of greatness. Your hands which would help you defeat the beast and climb the pit are used for other purposes. What happiness lies in such an existence? Your sword lies only a few feet away. The monster does not think you will take up your sword and fight. It has broke you. That is what you think. Yet it is there, only a little bit away. Perhaps, just maybe....
